snippet.title: Broventure: Roguelike Co-op Adventure Gameplay
snippet.description:
A roguelike co-op game where you and your friends can team up to face waves of enemies, unlock unique hero synergies, and build your own camp.

Learn more and wishlist at: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2939640/Broventure_The_Wild_Coop/

Follow us on socials:
X/Twitter: https://x.com/broventure_game
Discord: https://discord.gg/QCKqYk3FZr
